</p><p>They are complemented by six constraints on gating variables and ion concentrations: <disp-formula id="pcbi.1003941.e020"><graphic xlink:href="pcbi.1003941.e020.jpg" position="anchor" orientation="portrait"/><label>(7)</label></disp-formula>
